  "clauseName": "1.4.8.1_农产品精简版（20260422181920）",
  "clauseNumber": "1.4.8.1",
  "clauseContent": "1.4.8.1.  <span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">会计分录</span>\n<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">①移交蛋鸡给农户：</span>\n<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"> 借：生产性生物资产—蛋鸡(农户)</span>\n<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"> 贷：生产性生物资产—蛋鸡(场部)</span>\n<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">②发放饲料/兽药：</span>\n<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"> 借：消耗性生物资产—养殖成本</span>\n<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"> 贷：原材料</span>\n<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">③支付农户服务费：</span>\n<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"> 借：消耗性生物资产—养殖成本</span>\n<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"> 贷：银行存款</span>\n<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">④鸡蛋入库：</span>\n<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"> 借：库存商品—鸡蛋</span>\n<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"> 贷：消耗性生物资产—养殖成本</span>\n<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">⑤销售鸡蛋/淘汰鸡：</span>\n<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"> 确认收入并结转成本。</span>",
